props.askBeforeClosing: Determines whether to ask before closing.
props.closeOtherTabsText: The text of close other tabs.
props.closeTabsToTheLeftText: The text of close tabs to the left.
props.closeTabsToTheRightText: The text of close tabs to the right.
props.hideSlider: Determines whether to hide the slider.
props.noDataPath: The path to navigate to when there is no tabs.
props.onClose: Custom logic for closing tabs, returning `false` can prevent closing.
props.selfPatterns: Used for fuzzy matching paths. All successful paths are displayed in the same tab.

contents.tabIconContent: The fragment of the tab icon.
